Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:48.19,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算倒下千萬次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K28}立{\K45}ち{\K49}上{\K40}が{\K58}る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:53.39,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K18}こ{\K26}の{\K28}世{\K39}は{\K37}弱{\K71}肉{\K65}強{\K37}食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:53.39,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個弱肉強食的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K26}据{\K34}え{\K20}膳{\K85}食{\K28}う{\K34}よ{\K43}り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其坐享其成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:59.09,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K37}血{\K80}潮{\K87}奮っ{\K47}て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:59.09,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如憑著一腔激蕩熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K26}つ{\K53}か{\K42}み{\K33}と{\K56}れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拼命奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.94,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K66}賭{\K16}け{\K34}ろ{\K30}プ{\K40}ラ{\K34}イ{\K47}ド
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.94,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上尊嚴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.68,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K16}死{\K44}ぬ{\K30}ま{\K35}で{\K139}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.68,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至死都是一匹狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:13.69,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K38}負{\K32}け{\K71}犬{\K32}に{\K36}な{\K46}る{\K30}つ{\K25}も{\K17}り{\K55}は{\K27}な{\K71}い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:13.69,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從不打算成為喪家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.89,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K69}汗{\K37}は{\K29}ス{\K44}パ{\K25}イ{\K50}ス
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.89,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗水是調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.65,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K57}傷{\K55}跡{\K106}輝{\K47}く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.65,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷痕在閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.30,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K71}勝{\K44}利{\K37}の{\K63}味{\K45}を{\K34}か{\K31}み{\K49}し{\K32}め{\K43}て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:24.30,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細咀嚼著勝利的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:28.04,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K43}次{\K30}の{\K23}ス{\K41}テー{\K16}ジ{\K201}へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:28.04,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下一個舞臺邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤那家伙 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所以說...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和這裡的學生著莪菖蒲一起的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平易近人 對像我這樣的大叔都會每天早上打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 總有一天會有些自作多情的笨蛋跑出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所以說我說了好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰說什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲醬就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來教教你們接近她會有多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是塞進裏面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗人正企圖與堂弟佐藤洋接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 估計兩人是打算一起去狩獵便當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 狩獵場還沒弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？佐藤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙大概1個多小時以前在校門前面被警衛帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 我來塞進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了 二階堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來麗人和佐藤打算去拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤帶著傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你先過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我們的計劃的最終目的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅佐藤是計劃的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佐藤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來 你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是搞什麼 是快被搞定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上手機跑已經是用盡全力的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 拜託給我弄套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急情況 哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥你們要追著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑啊 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 衣服什麼的一件也沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼跑哪裡去了 我來塞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪 慢死了 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態 好變態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈辱啊 為什麼我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你個好東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下啦 坐下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個就能蓋住頭發 沒問題的 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這是怎麼個能行...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花紋是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是井上馬醉木 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬醉木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去自動販賣機買咖啡回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我請你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 突然間就...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我可是救了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 和馬醉木扯上關系你就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的不幸會降臨到你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是超自然現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說你不也碰到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬醉木身上纏著一股神佛都唯恐避之不及的不幸氣場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為啥突然間桌腳斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥這種地方會有圖釘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才給你戴上帽子的時候碰到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之早點遠離這裡比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也快到貼半價貼紙的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鞋的話隨便到鞋柜拿雙涼鞋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...不如去第二家超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來前天有說過吧 拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得從學姐手上拿到傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？學姐給的傳單去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難得從學姐手上拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧 學姐的傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 馬醉木她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 她的話一定不會回來的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不是咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以隨便喝耶 好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子一直在感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以才圍著圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人沒有覺得不幸也算是唯一的救贖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還和我的菖蒲醬親密地走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起來 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拖住大叔 你趕快去拉爾夫便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹輪我拿走了 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您10000零30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不不不 這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道啦 現在男生也會穿成這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說學姐你為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是齋藤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想承認是我對手的男人竟然會是這等變態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是不打算對別人的興趣多管閑事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 學姐你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態 變態 變態...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候說可愛的話算是贊美吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這是著莪那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌慌張張的 真不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這當中有著復雜的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有要跟你這種人說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一瞬間肯定了你的我真是蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 那個...也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人就等著被「帝王」打垮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...為啥那個人會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 「帝王」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」是指以這家店為地盤的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為求勝利不惜用盡卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的「狼」也認定他很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的「狼」在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是「帝王」的地盤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稱為西區「狼」的代表的你都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「帝王」之間形成抗爭的話要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無意引起和那家伙的爭端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大北海道展覽會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天早上拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量使用北海道食材的珍稀便當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周周五起3天的限定期間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 像這樣的便當在變成半價以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能剩下來都是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？白粉的校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我過去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 這個可以說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讓她也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你知道東區的拉爾夫便利店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦 肯定知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還校服之余順便...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確保什麼都不知道的佐藤不會向「帝王」出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過來看看情況而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 專門為了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 難道說對我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那個...怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種事也不怎麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的生活方式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說那個...不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤同學 拿出自信來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？你說什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 這家店的半價神來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人？而且還很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松葉菊 人稱小松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年以前還是相當有名的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後現在成了半價神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如學姐所說 北海道展覽會剩下的就只有那些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說也有幾個普通的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的目標果然還是石狩鮭魚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要鰻魚魚子便當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是魔女的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 你也是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊 麗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓你拿到便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是「加百列的棘齒」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「帝王」忠實的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「加百列的棘齒」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 那群人的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像是只為了攔住佐藤一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女養的「狗」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜你將會在歷史留名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到光榮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 已經分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把這男人當作東區和西區全面抗爭的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 「湖之麗人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這只沒用的雜種狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜種狗只要乖乖地被我玩弄於股掌之上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出最強之名的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的血化為開戰的狼煙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來後發現 我和不認識的女性在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我在不知不覺間登上了大人的階梯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 安定下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我預想的要快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 很快嗎我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...雖然我記不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我果然是打了一仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以有下次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨我記不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨自己的經驗不足到讓對方說結果很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來對方是人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果丈夫在這時候出現的話就成修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就這樣退縮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不管是快還是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用次數來彌補的話就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 還是年輕氣盛的我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 起來吧 我的小弟弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一直不醒的話 就只能背著你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？臉色很差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為「帝王」的攻擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你記憶有點混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是拉爾夫便利店的休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應半價神的好意 讓被「帝王」打倒的你在這裡休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這麼說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我把衣服帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快換上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...我有點難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話請你們兩位...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒什麼比你這幅樣子要更讓人難為情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快換上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說我現在起不來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 腳受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 學姐 那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了？發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 只有我被排斥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從某種意義上來說已經起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雖說買是買了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過咖啡過濾器有好幾種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我買了3種...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 一共多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全部人變成男人的話能用得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下這個了 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能請我吃東西已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃晚餐之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗人 我有事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和「帝王」是有什麼關系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說不上什麼關系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就告訴你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」打算把這條街的所有超市納入支配范圍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西區占領作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天算起 3天後的北海道展覽會最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「加百列的棘齒」為中心的西區的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會襲擊西區的所有超市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 「帝王」打算一次過算清以前的舊賬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的舊賬？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說被稱為東區最強的「狼」以前敗給了西區的「狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「帝王」對此事依然懷恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我是打算一跟佐藤重逢就馬上說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我又想 不如就先不說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也參與了那個計劃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知「帝王」埋伏在這裡 還是把佐藤帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那真的只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼不早點說出計劃的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為佐藤他...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤他...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我做什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在胸前好好想想 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們也得想個對策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊在3天後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 白粉 我需要你們的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是東區的「狼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡的話事情也不好說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有可能被盯上了 應該避免單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 看來對他們而言我就是只個棄子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著莪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那家伙罵我說雜種狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個我不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為我吧
