Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:56.32,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K66}強{\K40}く{\K138}結{\K32}び{\K37}つ{\K31}い{\K24}て{\K32}い{\K60}る
